<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="27May1927"><font color="red">SL, BL 27 May 1927</font> (to Sylvia Beach): I had a dreadful time with a savage dog on 25 inst. &hellip; If I could do the trick of gentleman into fox [see <a name="n03161k" href="../../ff/fnbs/n03all.htm#n03161k">N03 VI.B.3.161(k)</a>] I could save my breath better. &hellip; Thank Mrs Antheil [who was from Russia] for the words. I shall use some of them. </div>
